---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Coding Journey | Aarya Patel">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-6">

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="text-center py-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">💻 Coding Journey</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">My adventure in programming and problem-solving</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Python Mastery -->
    <Card title="Python Programming" emoji="🐍">
      <p class="mb-4">I've mastered the fundamentals of Python programming, including:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Data Types:</strong> Numbers, strings, lists, sets, and dictionaries</li>
        <li><strong>Conditionals:</strong> If/else statements for decision making</li>
        <li><strong>Loops:</strong> For loops and while loops for repetition</li>
        <li><strong>Functions:</strong> Creating reusable code blocks</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        I've built several projects to practice these concepts, including my Snake Game!
      </p>
    </Card>

    <!-- LeetCode Progress -->
    <Card title="LeetCode Practice" emoji="🧠">
      <p class="mb-4">I practice problem-solving on LeetCode regularly. It helps me think logically and learn new algorithms.</p>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">140+</p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Problems Solved</p>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4">
        <a
          href="https://leetcode.com/u/aarya142016/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          View My LeetCode Profile →
        </a>
      </p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Snake Game -->
    <Card title="My Snake Game" emoji="🎮">
      <p class="mb-4">One of my first big projects was building a classic Snake game using Python and Pygame!</p>
      <div class="bg-gray-100 dark:bg-slate-700 rounded-lg p-4 mb-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">How I Built It:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <li>Used Pygame for graphics and game loop</li>
          <li>Implemented snake movement with keyboard controls</li>
          <li>Added food spawning and score tracking</li>
          <li>Handled collision detection (walls and self)</li>
          <li>Added game over screen with restart option</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <p class="mb-4">The game runs right in the browser using PyScript!</p>
      <a
        href="/snake/snake.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-block px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg transition-colors"
      >
        Play Snake Game →
      </a>
    </Card>

    <!-- Future Goals -->
    <Card title="What's Next?" emoji="🚀">
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Learn more advanced algorithms and data structures</li>
        <li>Build more games and interactive projects</li>
        <li>Explore web development beyond static sites</li>
        <li>Continue solving LeetCode problems to improve my problem-solving skills</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <!-- Back to Home -->
    <div class="text-center pt-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
